name: Marado
description:
In a social network he was born, it was God's wish,
Grow and survive the humble expression.
Face adversity
With a desire to earn a living at every step.
In a pasture he forged an immortal left foot
Experienced thirsty ambition to get there.
As an onion I dreamed of playing a World Cup
And be consecrated in First,
Maybe playing I could
